                        <div class="post-heading">
                            <h1>Peering into the Potential of SETI</h1> 
                            <h2 class="subheading"></h2> 
                            <span class="meta">
                                Posted by 
                                <a href="">Deepthy Ajith K</a> 
                                on September 10, 2022
                            </span>
                            <span class="meta">
                                Edited by 
                                <a href="">Ishan Choudhary</a> 
